WEBVTT

00:03:56.757 --> 00:04:00.108
and I would be repatriated
to a horrible fate,

00:04:00.132 --> 00:04:01.826
back in North Korea.

00:04:02.969 --> 00:04:05.667
One day, my worst nightmare came true,

00:04:05.691 --> 00:04:08.414
when I was caught by the Chinese police,

00:04:08.438 --> 00:04:12.505
and brought to the police station
for interrogation.

00:04:12.529 --> 00:04:16.187
Someone had accused me
of being North Korean,

00:04:16.211 --> 00:04:19.592
so they tested my Chinese
language abilities,

00:04:19.616 --> 00:04:22.162
and asked me tons of questions.

00:04:22.910 --> 00:04:24.392
I was so scared.

00:04:25.352 --> 00:04:27.487
I thought my heart was going to explode.

00:04:28.164 --> 00:04:33.021
If anything seemed unnatural,
I could be imprisoned and repatriated.